{"tid":1859011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"*夢遊手足注意* 美國鑑證科警員證實 Android 手機較 iPhone 更難破解","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T01:35:46.000Z","uid":64745,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7f857bd3230e77b8c32eb61c5d56fd1b9bed4766","tid":1859011,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"智能手機裝著不少個人資料和通訊記錄，當執法機關需要進行調查時，往往都會從疑犯的智能手機入手。近期有不少新聞與 iPhone 被執法機關破解有關，日前有美國負責數碼鑑證的警員就透露，現時的 Android 手機比 iPhone 更難破解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自德州 Fort Worth 警區的數碼鑑證探員 Rex Kiser 接受訪問時，表示他們約一年前無法破解 iPhone，但可以破解任何 Android 手機，但現在並非所有 Android 手機都能破解。報導提到執法機構僱用專業的手機破解公司，當中最出名的 Cellebrite 擁有能夠破解包括 iPhone X 在內手機的工具，它能夠抓住 GPS 位置、訊息、通話記錄、聯絡人資訊，甚至 Instagram、Twitter、LinkedIn 等程式的數據，有助進行檢控工作。<br />\n<br />\n報導指 Cellebrite 的工具在對付 Android 手機的加密技術，就未如 iPhone 般成功，例如 Google Pixel 2、Samsung Galaxy S9、華為 P20 Pro 都不對應，無法取得社交媒體、瀏覽或 GPS 資料。雖然 Cellebrite 的工具在 Android 層面比較遜色，但並不代表 Android 無從破解，只是花費的時間和資源較多。<br />\n<br />\n來源：androidauthority<br />\n<br />\n並唔係想踩iphone或者引戰or whatever，只想提供翻客觀資料，唔好一本通書睇到老，以為以前an機lag同易破解就代表而家都係。<br />\n<br />\n同場加送 資安公司 Gartner security呢幾年對mobile platform安全嘅評測， 三星同pixel整體得分比ios高<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.informationweek.com/mobile/mobile-devices/samsung-knox-security-beats-ios-android-gartner-finds/d/d-id/1325145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.informationweek.com%2Fmobile%2Fmobile-devices%2Fsamsung-knox-security-beats-ios-android-gartner-finds%2Fd%2Fd-id%2F1325145&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=75bede46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.informationweek.com/mobile/mobile-devices/samsung-knox-security-beats-ios-android-gartner-finds/d/d-id/1325145</a><br />\n<br />\nLm睇一定有人話三星360送中嘅Reddit post，但爭議點在於到底回傳嘅資料係咪你嘅個人資料而係真係for database check嘅資料？po主無解密到個patch就貿然開po，大家係跟風之前最好都加啲個人思考。 講到底，作為美國國防部許可政府人員用嘅手機，我唔認為三星真係有將你個人資料送中，除非國防部班友係盲嘅，係審核過程中睇住佢回傳而唔會睇傳啲咩資料走"},{"pid":"7e2c431c7defa8b65cc409719ae93888d69fac16","tid":1859011,"uid":319606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"【撐醫護】屌打撕紙狗！全港最大連儂牆正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1859012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1859012</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"784d4796813ba59ed3821a040ad2c0a9a63455fd","tid":1859011,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef32a9d09fad4e71fc3d9af6c6223da77757cfd6","tid":1859011,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784d4796813ba59ed3821a040ad2c0a9a63455fd","tid":1859011,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"美國鑑證科警員證實   Android 手機較 iPhone 更難破解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1858822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1858822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8d398c1abf0f7ded54fe19ef2d5511e7e11cc96","tid":1859011,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"android 好碎片化, engineer出samsung 又要搞huawei, 仲有LG sony......<br />\n<a href=\"https://source.android.com/security/encryption/full-disk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsource.android.com%2Fsecurity%2Fencryption%2Ffull-disk&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7c538761\" target=\"_blank\">https://source.android.com/security/encryption/full-disk</a><br />\nbased on DMcrypt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d696fd36bc0bd86a290348a177bed60ad85805cf","tid":1859011,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"等睇ifanboy出黎解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb314eb1b3a6c1d45a1f62b32f14279d13cf06f5","tid":1859011,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d696fd36bc0bd86a290348a177bed60ad85805cf","t